gn lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">αἷμα ἔσχεθον</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">staunched</tr_> it, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:19:458\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">19.458</biblScope> </bibl>: c. gen., <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">σχέθε δ᾽ ὄσσε γόοιο</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:4:758\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.758</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὅπως ἂν αὐτὰς ὕβρεως σχέθω</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg007.perseus-grc1:425\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lys.\">Lys.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">425</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0005.tlg001.perseus-grc1:22:96\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Theoc.\">Theoc.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">22.96</biblScope> </bibl>: c. <mood opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"mood\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ part.\">part.</a></mood>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐρέφοντα σχέθοι</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">might stop</tr_> him from wreathing, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0033.tlg004.perseus-grc1:4(3).54(72)\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pi.\">Pi.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ I.\">I.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4(3).54(72)</biblScope> </bibl>: c. <mood opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"mood\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ inf.\">inf.</a></mood>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">οὔτ᾽ ἂν Αἴαντος δόρυ μὴ πάντα πέρσαι . . σχέθοι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0006.tlg019.perseus-grc1:602\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Rh.\">Rh.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">602</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"III\" id=\"n101827.3\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> abs., <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">οὐδ᾽ ἄρ᾽ ὀχῆες ἐσχεθέτην</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">did</tr_> not <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">hold</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:12:461\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">12.461</biblScope></bibl>.--Rare in Prose, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0719.tlg003.perseus-grc1:2:4\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Aret.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ CA\">CA</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.4</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}